high_descs: walk to the end of the room on the right, then turn right and walk to the other end of the room past the oven
grab a cup from the bottom left cabinet
turn right and walk over to the fridge at the end of the room
place the cup inside of the fridge to cool, then take it back out
turn left and walk forwards, then turn left and walk to the microwave, but turn right to face the coffee maker next to the microwave on the right
place the cup inside of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: place a cooled cup under the spout of the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn right, go toward the wall, turn right again and go straight toward the counter with the coffee maker.
Take the mug from the cabinet under the coffee maker.
Turn right, go straight, turn right, then turn left to face the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Turn left, move forward, turn left, go forward toward the dishwasher, then turn right to face the counter with the coffee maker.
Place the mug at the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a cool mug at the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn right, cross the room until you reach the wall, hang a right until you reach the coffee maker on the counter.
Open the cabinet door beneath the coffee maker, pick up the white mug behind the clear glass from inside the cabinet, and close the door.
Turn right, cross the room, hang a right at the counter and turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the mug inside on the top shelf in the middle, close the door to let the mug chill for seven seconds, open the door, pick up the mug and close the door.
Turn left, cross the room until you reach the counter, hang a left and turn right to face the coffee maker on the counter top.
Place the mug onto the silver platform underneath the nozzle of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug onto the coffee maker.
